### Create a Tournament
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Spring Handball Tournament",
  "date": "2025-03-15",
  "description": "An exciting spring tournament for all skill levels."
}

### Get All Tournaments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments

### Get a Tournament by ID (assume ID is 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments/1

### Update a Tournament (change name)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Tournament Name",
  "date": "2025-03-15",
  "description": "An updated description for the tournament."
}

### Delete a Tournament
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tournaments/4
